<div class="container features">
    <h1 class="mt-3 mb-5 fw-bold text-center">Features of Himalayan Blog</h1>
    
    <h2>User-Friendly Interface</h2>
    <p>Our blog web application boasts an intuitive and user-friendly interface, making it easy for users of all skill levels to navigate and find the content they need. The clean design and responsive layout ensure a seamless experience across all devices, whether you're on a desktop, tablet, or smartphone.</p>

    <h2>Rich Text Editor</h2>
    <p>Crafting beautiful blog posts is a breeze with our rich text editor. It supports a wide range of formatting options, including bold, italics, bullet points, numbered lists, hyperlinks, and more. You can also embed images, videos, and other media to make your posts more engaging and interactive.</p>

    <h2>Category and Tag Management</h2>
    <p>Organize your content efficiently with our category and tag management system. Assign posts to multiple categories and tags to help readers find related content quickly. This feature enhances the overall user experience and boosts the SEO performance of your blog.</p>

    <h2>SEO Optimization</h2>
    <p>Improve the visibility of your blog on search engines with built-in SEO optimization tools. Customize meta titles, descriptions, and keywords for each post, and take advantage of our SEO analysis to ensure your content is optimized for search engines.</p>

    <h2>Commenting System</h2>
    <p>Engage with your audience through our robust commenting system. Readers can leave comments on your posts, ask questions, and share their thoughts. You have full control over comment moderation, allowing you to approve, delete, or reply to comments as needed.</p>

    <h2>Social Media Integration</h2>
    <p>Extend the reach of your content with social media integration. Share your posts on popular social media platforms with just a click, and add social sharing buttons to your posts to encourage readers to spread the word.</p>

    <h2>Analytics Dashboard</h2>
    <p>Track the performance of your blog with our comprehensive analytics dashboard. Monitor key metrics such as page views, unique visitors, and engagement rates. Use these insights to refine your content strategy and grow your audience.</p>

    <h2>Customizable Themes</h2>
    <p>Personalize your blog with customizable themes. Choose from a variety of pre-designed themes, or create your own to match your brand’s aesthetic. Customize colors, fonts, and layouts to give your blog a unique and professional look.</p>

    <h2>Newsletter Subscription</h2>
    <p>Build and nurture your readership with our newsletter subscription feature. Collect email addresses from your visitors and send out regular updates, new posts, and special announcements directly to their inboxes.</p>

    <h2>Content Scheduling</h2>
    <p>Plan your content ahead of time with our content scheduling feature. Write posts in advance and set them to be published on specific dates and times. This ensures a consistent posting schedule, even when you’re busy.</p>

    <h2>Multi-Author Support</h2>
    <p>Collaborate with other writers and contributors with multi-author support. Assign different roles and permissions to authors, editors, and admins, and manage your content team effectively.</p>

    <h2>Security and Backup</h2>
    <p>Keep your blog secure with advanced security measures, including SSL encryption and regular backups. Your content is safe from unauthorized access and data loss, giving you peace of mind.</p>

    <h2>Mobile App</h2>
    <p>Stay connected on the go with our mobile app. Write and publish posts, moderate comments, and track analytics directly from your smartphone or tablet, ensuring you’re never far from your blog.</p>
